    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔前往国会山：预期情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/powell-heads-to-capitol-hill-what-to-expect-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗高级全球经济学家罗伯特·索金 (Robert Sockin) 预测了美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔本周在美国众议院和参议院的证词。索金在接受“彭博社收盘”采访时表示，他预计美联储将在 9 月份降息。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-08/powell-heads-to-capitol-hill-what-to-expect-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 08 Jul 2024 20:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
